commit_message:
Overhaul ceilometer utils unit tests

* Use the new client mocking instead of FakeCeilometerClient, which
  split expected values into a separate module and depended on the
  FakeCeilometerClient implementation being correct;
* Add atomic action timer tests to tests;
* Improved some tests;
* Miscellaneous cleanup;
* A few minor fixes to the utils code.

Change-Id: Ifb8c21a115a6c358b432504b3fc9505ae8575b6f
